00:20:02.820 --> 00:20:04.120
&gt;&gt; Ronald L. Smith:
Oh, my God, did I.

00:20:04.120 --> 00:20:05.420
&gt;&gt; [Laughs].

00:20:05.420 --> 00:20:06.720
&gt;&gt; Ronald L. Smith:
I can't tell you.

