They're really scary.

00:20:08.020 --> 00:20:09.320
&gt;&gt; Tell me, please.

00:20:09.320 --> 00:20:10.620
&gt;&gt; Ronald L. Smith:
I was kind of bad.

00:20:10.620 --> 00:20:14.690
One time I rode my
bike down the hill

00:20:14.690 --> 00:20:18.920
because somebody dared
me to and I broke my arm.

00:20:18.920 --> 00:20:20.220
So don't ever do that.

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:21.910
Do what your mom and
dad tell you to do.

00:20:21.910 --> 00:20:23.210
